
espeak talking in Korean!
https://github.com/puzzlet/espeak-korean

install espeak and dependencies
sudo apt-get install espeak espeakedit make python

then
git clone --recursive git://github.com/puzzlet/espeak-korean.git
cd espeak-korean
sudo make
make speak

then check that you have Korean in your espeak voices options:
espeak --voices=

should list Korean between kannada and kurdish
if so you're good to go;

espeak "바다는, 크레파스보다 진한, 푸르고 육중한 비늘을 무겁게 뒤채면서, 숨을 쉰다.l" -v Korean

options? 
espeak --h
